{"tid":1542803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"閘住！我識果位粉嶺女義士唔係今日生日喎！","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:59:34.000Z","uid":143167,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"76d196cbb141abc5a6120cd82696a67fd464bdc3","tid":1542803,"uid":143167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"我唔知大家係咪見到場波由0比5勉強算係追到1比4就得意忘形，見到有post就想推，抑或係我太過平行時空唔睇新聞，連粉嶺有第二位失去生命嘅女義士都唔識。<br />\n<br />\n總之呢，我認識果位粉嶺女義士叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盧曉欣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n假如你有幸係佢生前八百幾個facebook好友之一，又或者願意稍移玉步去佢ig睇下，就會知道佢嘅生日係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3月27日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ck99eXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCk99eXX.jpg&h=237cbe2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lohiuyan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flohiuyan%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=a724bb66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lohiuyan/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後留番條東方日報link比大家對下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190629/bkn-20190629163435030-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190629%2Fbkn-20190629163435030-0629_00822_001.html&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=f4d4e187\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190629/bkn-20190629163435030-0629_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：同佢捉過rummikub，希望大家有果句講果句，唔好老作。另外假如真係有第二位粉嶺女義士，記得同我講，我欠佢一句RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622b67c4d8fee1e2d1cb5ea87c5996d33da0e8ae","tid":1542803,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:33:43.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/153557